<document>
  <header>
    <title>Xml Code Completion</title>
    <authors>
      <person name="Eric Van Dewoestine" email="ervandew@yahoo.com"/>
    </authors>
  </header>
  <body>
    <p>
      Xml code completion uses the standard
      <a href="../code_completion.html">Vim code completion mechanism</a> like
      so:
    </p>
    <source>
      <![CDATA[
      <ser<Ctrl-X><Ctrl-U>

      <servlet>
        <ser<Ctrl-X><Ctrl-U>

      <servlet>
        <servlet-name>
      ...
      ]]>
    </source>
    <note>
      Requires a valid dtd or xsd to determine possible completions.<br/>
      Requires the <a href="site:eclipse_wst">eclipse wst plugin</a>.
    </note>
  </body>
</document>
